Package uk.ac.susx.mlcl.lib

A library of miscellaneous Java code, likely to be useful for many of the MLCL Lab projects.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
C14nCache<T> The C14nCache (canonicalisation cache) is used to reduce the number of redundant copies of identical objects in memory.
Checks Static utility class used for checking method arguments.
Comparators A static utility class for creating, and manipulating Comparator objects.
MathUtil Utility class to hold a number of static maths functions.
MemoryUsage Class to calculate the approximate memory usage of java objects.
MiscUtil MiscUtil is a static utility class for methods that don't fit anywhere else.
Strings Static utility class for String manipulation.
ZipfianDistribution Class that provides methods to calculate the PMF, CDF, and Quantile functions of a Zipfian (power law) distribution.
 

Enum Summary
